Citing
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

When referencing this work in an academic publication, we ask that you cite the following source:

* Ivanova, Sardana, Francis M. Tyers, and Jonathan N. Washington (2021).  **A Prototype Free/Open-Source Morphological Analyser and Generator for Sakha**.  Presented at _WiNLP 2021 Workshop, EMNLP 2021_.  (Links to poster and abstract to appear.)

